name: Metakings
public_notice: We've received allegations that the team has abandoned the project/Rugpull. Please proceed with extreme caution.
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: Metakings is an AI-powered fighting universe in which anyone can earn rewards such as tokens and NFTs through competent gameplay and contributions to the ecosystem. Players can engage in combat, gather resources, develop their characters, and establish their own land-based kingdoms.
